com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.networking.ethernet

Class Network

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.BaseModelResource
      • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.networking.ethernet.Network
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Network
extends BaseModelResource
    The Network data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent a vlan in the system. It is passed in to the add/update network REST api, as well as the add/update network through java client api.
